    h3 We are The Washington University Aristocats.
    p.
      We are <strong>The Washington University Aristocats</strong>, Wash U’s all-Disney a cappella group, and we’ve been wreaking havoc since 2005. It’s a simple formula: find several reasonably attractive college kids who take singing seriously (and not much else), give them Disney music to sing, and you’ve got a group that makes people smile. We attempt strange accents, try to imitate animals (specifically lorded felines), and, most importantly, spread Disney magic wherever we go, all in the name of avoiding homework and making people happier.
    p.text-center
      a(href="/music.html") Learn what we sing &rarr;
    p.text-center
      a(href="/auditions.html") Join us &rarr;
